item.title: [HIVE-22976] Oracle and MSSQL upgrade script missing the addition of WM_RESOURCEPLAN_FK1 constraint
item.description: The schema init script (>=hive-schema-3.0.0) contains a constraint addition, which is missing from the upgrade scripts in oracle and mssql.
item.summary: Oracle and MSSQL upgrade script missing the addition of WM_RESOURCEPLAN_FK1 constraint

status.description: The issue is considered finished, the resolution is correct. Issues which are not closed can be reopened.
